{"tid":2428113,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【墮樓意外】女兒失足從2樓墮下壓凹車頂　哭訴爸爸沒慰問只關心車子：心都碎了","createTime":"2021-03-01T10:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T10:50:02.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5251beb707061cc98e5f3c43d76d98fdad344e59","tid":2428113,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:12:24.000Z","msg":"不少男士愛車，甚至視車子比女兒更重要。台灣一名女大學生日前在網上討論區發文，指她不慎從家中2樓墮下，撞到私家車頂部，造成車頂凹陷；爸爸回來看見後，沒有安慰女兒，反而第一時間關心車子狀況，令女兒感到心酸。<br />\n<br />\n事件發生在上週五，樓主在文中指出，自己當時打算拿回掉在2樓窗外的衣物，卻不慎墜樓，跌落至1樓車庫，造成車棚及車頂受損，自己的手臂及大腿亦擦傷。然而，爸爸回來之後，卻沒有慰問女兒，反而第一時間關心車子狀況，不斷跟她說「車才剛保養完」、「車棚很貴」等，又罵女兒很蠢。<br />\n<br />\n樓主聽後感到傷心，心想「你都知道車頂凹陷了，難道我會沒受傷嗎？為什麼不是先關心我的身體？我又不是不會賠，只關心那些身外之物，好糟的爸爸。」她默默地流淚，爸爸見狀才慰問她，她回答「沒事」之後回房間大哭。<br />\n<br />\n她事後發文奉勸，如果身邊的朋友、愛人、家人一時疏忽造成意外，應該第一時間給予對方關心，並非責罵，畢竟受傷、用壞物品都不是自己願意，<br />\n&quot;你先關心物品，她內心的傷也是一輩子的。&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2885000/2889102/car_thumb_20210301_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2885000%2F2889102%2Fcar_thumb_20210301_ch_1024.jpg&h=de3150d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95b5623d9e3f183ea4d4f4931d460fcac60b0dee","tid":2428113,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:15:54.000Z","msg":"隻腳瘀到.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67b353e524150fe865c479a9678736929890dce","tid":2428113,"uid":47643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:17:06.000Z","msg":"新北1分"},{"pid":"307634aa3d171e0e31bbdbe90d6eb02d9f4e5072","tid":2428113,"uid":17405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:17:28.000Z","msg":"你死好啦唔好整爛我架車"},{"pid":"3edf11606f713b28c3fb6dda0a3fe33ed8be6f6f","tid":2428113,"uid":36915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:18:29.000Z","msg":"今晚爸爸屌到佢大肚<br />\n這就是台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c654c3886ed1280144e270e425c208df6bbd34","tid":2428113,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:18:34.000Z","msg":"真係唔知點做人父母，架車比個女重要，果然係叻嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1adbaa7ae1ba70a5a1df69d49fa0c450f96f373","tid":2428113,"uid":140363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:25:54.000Z","msg":"有事去左醫院探你<br />\n<br />\n返得嚟喺屋企即係人無事<br />\n<br />\n咁咪去關心架車"},{"pid":"9347d51b28949339ff3524a708f77992ed5019ad","tid":2428113,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:27:01.000Z","msg":"個女係咪好丑？"},{"pid":"ca522aa6a2e7dc3eb7c40796b30278608af1588a","tid":2428113,"uid":349494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:50:02.000Z","msg":"整爛我㗎車仲要我安慰你，唔踢你出街都偷笑啦"}]}